23b75b797a37c1f4b54a","tid":374063,"uid":60048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"18dse 留名"},{"pid":"803b44c4df494887057d545d15ba92fd73be6809","tid":374063,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"其實畫圖咪解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd3a8453411b31c32ec77cb5eb771584280b794","tid":374063,"uid":135395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"我唔識個3題撞中0題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後竟然有星星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f926010c9adc57100a2405f4f699221c01478b","tid":374063,"uid":18786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實畫圖咪解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫完都要諗到先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c9ba21bf86de52802fe2063cd6c1e0d9214ec1","tid":374063,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"1. 講解得尚算清楚<br />\n<br />\n2. 美中不足嘅係 由 tan &theta; = 3/4 去搵 tan 2&theta; = 24/7 呢一步用咗計數機，原則上只可以當係 approximation 唔可以當係 exact value。<br />\n唔用計數機嘅話最直接就係用 tangent 嘅 double angle formula，但可惜係 M2 嘢。<br />\n要用返 compulsory 範圍內嘅嘢都唔係無辦法，係要一個稍為巧妙嘅處理。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實用 inscribed circle 都可以做到。你話會諗極都諗唔到稍有誤導之嫌。<br />\n我講個 outline 啦<br />\n設 I 係個 incentre 而 r 係個 inscribed circle 嘅 radius<br />\n咁 I 嘅坐標其實係 (r,r)<br />\n由於 I 喺 3x+4y=3p 上面，可以做到 r = 3p/7<br />\n之後用 Area of OPI + Area of OQI + Area of PQI = Area of OPQ<br />\n做到 1/2*p*r+1/2*q*r+1/2*sqrt(p^2+q^2)*r = 1/2*p*q<br />\nsub 返 r = 3p/7 再爆一輪就會出到答案<br />\n<br />\n4.「OK」好似講得少咗，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b72ca22d8f1349b1873e041fb0f0bd1357cd3a","tid":374063,"uid":113328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>18dse 留名</blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd692ed9fe0e5571757e16fbcb3a8be1d9faca68","tid":374063,"uid":113328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 講解得尚算清楚<br />\n<br />\n2. 美中不足嘅係 由 tan &theta; = 3/4 去搵 tan 2&theta; = 24/7 呢一步用咗計數機，原則上只可以當係 approximation 唔可以當係 exact value。<br />\n唔用計數機嘅話最直接就係用 tangent 嘅 double angle formula，但可惜係 M2 嘢。<br />\n要用返 compulsory 範圍內嘅嘢都唔係無辦法，係要一個稍為巧妙嘅處理。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實用 inscribed circle 都可以做到。你話會諗極都諗唔到稍有誤導之嫌。<br />\n我講個 outline 啦<br />\n設 I 係個 incentre 而 r 係個 inscribed circle 嘅 radius<br />\n咁 I 嘅坐標其實係 (r,r)<br />\n由於 I 喺 3x+4y=3p 上面，可以做到 r = 3p/7<br />\n之後用 Area of OPI + Area of OQI + Area of PQI = Area of OPQ<br />\n做到 1/2*p*r+1/2*q*r+1/2*sqrt(p^2+q^2)*r = 1/2*p*q<br />\nsub 返 r = 3p/7 再爆一輪就會出到答案<br />\n<br />\n4.「OK」好似講得少咗，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打再一次捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嘅做法都值得參考下 但我覺得比較難諗到<br />\n我之所以話諗極都諗唔到係因為我試過俾好多學生做過<br />\n真係有9成都係咁畫完出黎就望住個 inscribed circle 唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d96789fedb195c5731ad9395186df35f06ad830","tid":374063,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 講解得尚算清楚<br />\n<br />\n2. 美中不足嘅係 由 tan &theta; = 3/4 去搵 tan 2&theta; = 24/7 呢一步用咗計數機，原則上只可以當係 approximation 唔可以當係 exact value。<br />\n唔用計數機嘅話最直接就係用 tangent 嘅 double angle formula，但可惜係 M2 嘢。<br />\n要用返 compulsory 範圍內嘅嘢都唔係無辦法，係要一個稍為巧妙嘅處理。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實用 inscribed circle 都可以做到。你話會諗極都諗唔到稍有誤導之嫌。<br />\n我講個 outline 啦<br />\n設 I 係個 incentre 而 r 係個 inscribed circle 嘅 radius<br />\n咁 I 嘅坐標其實係 (r,r)<br />\n由於 I 喺 3x+4y=3p 上面，可以做到 r = 3p/7<br />\n之後用 Area of OPI + Area of OQI + Area of PQI = Area of OPQ<br />\n做到 1/2*p*r+1/2*q*r+1/2*sqrt(p^2+q^2)*r = 1/2*p*q<br />\nsub 返 r = 3p/7 再爆一輪就會出到答案<br />\n<br />\n4.「OK」好似講得少咗，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打再一次捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嘅做法都值得參考下 但我覺得比較難諗到<br />\n我之所以話諗極都諗唔到係因為我試過俾好多學生做過<br />\n真係有9成都係咁畫完出黎就望住個 inscribed circle 唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然係號稱最難MC咁諗唔到都好正常嘅<br />\n不過喺學生已經畫得出個 inscribed circle 嘅情況下，究竟係<br />\n1.跟返學生已有嘅思路，利用個 inscribed circle 完成條題目<br />\n2.提出一個學生意想不到嘅想法，例如係用 inclination 完成條題目<br />\n邊個做法會好啲呢？<br />\n我都諗唔到邊個會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd0b15ef393a7f6c77ae840e9c3b6af33d88a61","tid":374063,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實畫圖咪解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畫完都要諗到先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得架，不過高技考，屙緊屎，夜啲畫比你睇"},{"pid":"2a4170f298cac6a06e109076fce269b2c69ab12f","tid":374063,"uid":113328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ad43a2cb1f97656193f2251575f413eabfc5a7","tid":374063,"uid":45089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/231216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F231216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=961d478b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22ce7f6153b6e6dba05aba5d3326578225c1e489","tid":374063,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Hi, simon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhi 六常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你真人又幾靚仔啵"},{"pid":"172dc26b3828959620001806d40e345261d27944","tid":374063,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 講解得尚算清楚<br />\n<br />\n2. 美中不足嘅係 由 tan &theta; = 3/4 去搵 tan 2&theta; = 24/7 呢一步用咗計數機，原則上只可以當係 approximation 唔可以當係 exact value。<br />\n唔用計數機嘅話最直接就係用 tangent 嘅 double angle formula，但可惜係 M2 嘢。<br />\n要用返 compulsory 範圍內嘅嘢都唔係無辦法，係要一個稍為巧妙嘅處理。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實用 inscribed circle 都可以做到。你話會諗極都諗唔到稍有誤導之嫌。<br />\n我講個 outline 啦<br />\n設 I 係個 incentre 而 r 係個 inscribed circle 嘅 radius<br />\n咁 I 嘅坐標其實係 (r,r)<br />\n由於 I 喺 3x+4y=3p 上面，可以做到 r = 3p/7<br />\n之後用 Area of OPI + Area of OQI + Area of PQI = Area of OPQ<br />\n做到 1/2*p*r+1/2*q*r+1/2*sqrt(p^2+q^2)*r = 1/2*p*q<br />\nsub 返 r = 3p/7 再爆一輪就會出到答案<br />\n<br />\n4.「OK」好似講得少咗，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打再一次捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嘅做法都值得參考下 但我覺得比較難諗到<br />\n我之所以話諗極都諗唔到係因為我試過俾好多學生做過<br />\n真係有9成都係咁畫完出黎就望住個 inscribed circle 唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一開始諗係直接用 slope <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> In circle 有啲複雜同多啲時間"},{"pid":"5ef409b12d368f4bf2d7d5be7912edc7b6a80fb0","tid":374063,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/231216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F231216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=961d478b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea26cf376d2677149883749f4435756fd0e5989","tid":374063,"uid":131484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得今年math mc整體難左，無時間check，平日校內試或做卷都未試過，我呢題都係撞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：17DSE考生"},{"pid":"74986f592b79971697e88e5797a70c9c7f037350","tid":374063,"uid":114159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 講解得尚算清楚<br />\n<br />\n2. 美中不足嘅係 由 tan &theta; = 3/4 去搵 tan 2&theta; = 24/7 呢一步用咗計數機，原則上只可以當係 approximation 唔可以當係 exact value。<br />\n唔用計數機嘅話最直接就係用 tangent 嘅 double angle formula，但可惜係 M2 嘢。<br />\n要用返 compulsory 範圍內嘅嘢都唔係無辦法，係要一個稍為巧妙嘅處理。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實用 inscribed circle 都可以做到。你話會諗極都諗唔到稍有誤導之嫌。<br />\n我講個 outline 啦<br />\n設 I 係個 incentre 而 r 係個 inscribed circle 嘅 radius<br />\n咁 I 嘅坐標其實係 (r,r)<br />\n由於 I 喺 3x+4y=3p 上面，可以做到 r = 3p/7<br />\n之後用 Area of OPI + Area of OQI + Area of PQI = Area of OPQ<br />\n做到 1/2*p*r+1/2*q*r+1/2*sqrt(p^2+q^2)*r = 1/2*p*q<br />\nsub 返 r = 3p/7 再爆一輪就會出到答案<br />\n<br />\n4.「OK」好似講得少咗，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個inscribed circle用tangent properties快啲wo ching<br />\n我望住幅圖5分鐘先識tan slope 考試應該會sub數做<br />\n數學真係要打好個底"},{"pid":"a066586085a05f590e4b4e3cd47f8a348f01bbb2","tid":374063,"uid":65789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:44:50.000Z","msg":"真係落場做個時<br />\n得1分鐘做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又畫圖又盛 做到都真係幾勁"},{"pid":"249920350a9e672b343513cec1a70b6fccecaf23","tid":374063,"uid":134907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用cal program搵incenter<br />\n遂個答案dook = 輕鬆解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">利申 當時由a試起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都算做得耐</span>"},{"pid":"e8162db98cd43cd48e5d3fe68605c1408de7f22a","tid":374063,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T21:36:42.000Z","msg":"老老實實 考評局考四心不嬲都係用cal prog去就計到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ca5779ca5ea61d4c94160a9c5ef6a41cc995bd","tid":374063,"uid":2965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T21:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用cal program搵incenter<br />\n遂個答案dook = 輕鬆解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">利申 當時由a試起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都算做得耐</span></blockquote><br />\n我今年自修去玩都係用計數機去代數<br />\n最後都用左一分鐘先撞到d係岩<br />\n<br />\n最後45/45"},{"pid":"d698ce0d2fb926ecd0ad20ee57253a07e9212998","tid":374063,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 講解得尚算清楚<br />\n<br />\n2. 美中不足嘅係 由 tan &theta; = 3/4 去搵 tan 2&theta; = 24/7 呢一步用咗計數機，原則上只可以當係 approximation 唔可以當係 exact value。<br />\n唔用計數機嘅話最直接就係用 tangent 嘅 double angle formula，但可惜係 M2 嘢。<br />\n要用返 compulsory 範圍內嘅嘢都唔係無辦法，係要一個稍為巧妙嘅處理。<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實用 inscribed circle 都可以做到。你話會諗極都諗唔到稍有誤導之嫌。<br />\n我講個 outline 啦<br />\n設 I 係個 incentre 而 r 係個 inscribed circle 嘅 radius<br />\n咁 I 嘅坐標其實係 (r,r)<br />\n由於 I 喺 3x+4y=3p 上面，可以做到 r = 3p/7<br />\n之後用 Area of OPI + Area of OQI + Area of PQI = Area of OPQ<br />\n做到 1/2*p*r+1/2*q*r+1/2*sqrt(p^2+q^2)*r = 1/2*p*q<br />\nsub 返 r = 3p/7 再爆一輪就會出到答案<br />\n<br />\n4.「OK」好似講得少咗，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個inscribed circle用tangent properties快啲wo ching<br />\n我望住幅圖5分鐘先識tan slope 考試應該會sub數做<br />\n數學真係要打好個底</blockquote><br />\n用咗應該可以將 sqrt(p^2+q^2) 變做 (p + q - 2r)<br />\n係會輕鬆小小嘅<br />\n不過整體相差不遠"},{"pid":"8e109325c6b593ddb338494b0d63bea55f95879a","tid":374063,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得今年math mc整體難左，無時間check，平日校內試或做卷都未試過，我呢題都係撞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：17DSE考生</blockquote><br />\n整體難度無乜變，係好多題目無哂數字令學生hang機<br />\n如果學生唔係鳩用program嘅話，其實影響不大<br />\n<br />\n不過的確會用多咗時間<br />\n我今年完卷時間遲咗五分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d5aac0fe7cd7596e9618aa8acef99129c19906","tid":374063,"uid":135877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"諗到angle bisector 之後就諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後唔夠時間諗 驚到求鳩其咁當咗佢隻角係兩倍slope就係兩倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0443618db1b3fec90df0919544c1d309f0eea0f","tid":374063,"uid":135877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗到angle bisector 之後就諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後唔夠時間諗 驚到求鳩其咁當咗佢隻角係兩倍slope就係兩倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw 巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你解釋得好清楚"},{"pid":"151d21835630870654287f15e687b2483a338209","tid":374063,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗到angle bisector 之後就諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後唔夠時間諗 驚到求鳩其咁當咗佢隻角係兩倍slope就係兩倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n逆向思考一下<br />\n如果你明知道隻角係兩倍slope就一定唔係兩倍嘅話<br />\n咁3/2好明顯就唔係正確答案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b81595990e410f4df92345a4d0cee3f8a19df0","tid":374063,"uid":135877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗到angle bisector 之後就諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後唔夠時間諗 驚到求鳩其咁當咗佢隻角係兩倍slope就係兩倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n逆向思考一下<br />\n如果你明知道隻角係兩倍slope就一定唔係兩倍嘅話<br />\n咁3/2好明顯就唔係正確答案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我嗰陣好撚驚又冇乜時間淨 所以冇諗清楚 求其搏一鋪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b15ffb8612d849cf0fc8595cc02888a053fb689","tid":374063,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係落場做個時<br />\n得1分鐘做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又畫圖又盛 做到都真係幾勁</blockquote><br />\n你畫開就唔會慢<br />\n<br />\n秘訣：想搵 p:q 就set p , 畫番q 出嚟<br />\n三角4心果啲線要識點重現返"},{"pid":"b2c0f5c39d1865934f9aff06017c42e9cef08228","tid":374063,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e79d936c7e446fe42fa66ca38bc8fc1e10cdd98","tid":374063,"uid":113328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用cal program搵incenter<br />\n遂個答案dook = 輕鬆解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">利申 當時由a試起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都算做得耐</span></blockquote><br />\n呢個都係另一個幾快嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔想下下都教篤機好似無咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7036fafe1bda85a07b4f45dea96ca032960f1609","tid":374063,"uid":113328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔太難呢一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2d20a0c3f9e2412a559e32274f3b2f9117eaea","tid":374063,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔太難呢一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跪求難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570557c3bdf7e19d0a9e40c887e9102ab4cdbf22","tid":374063,"uid":114159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔太難呢一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跪求難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇2013 Q39<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2efbb34523770a35124a5d77d48f286ffc1a93","tid":374063,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔太難呢一題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跪求難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇2013 Q39<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDSE嚟講肯定算係名題級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1ce00f423847e5c4e10c6da56c9097294825e2","tid":374063,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"3x + 4y = p<br />\ny=(-3/4)x + 3/4 p<br />\nlet q/p = tan 2a, p/q = tan 2b<br />\ntan a = (3/4 p)/p = 3/4<br />\ntan 2a = 2(3/4)/(1-(3/4)^2) = 24/7<br />\nsince 2a = 90 - 2b<br />\ntan(90 - 2b) = 1/tan b = 24/7 <br />\np/q = tan b = 7/24<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8190ac0ff268e08068ef216c647c14c2d8946504","tid":374063,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:38:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f252298c62203c2521325da1c47ea377371eb2e","tid":374063,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想教probability 有冇人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg